data.name: AnalyzerMessageFormat
data.value: Required member(s) '{0}' must be initialized in type '{1}'

data.name: AnalyzerDescription
data.value: All members marked with [Required] must be initialized.

data.name: InvalidOptionalMemberMessageFormat
data.value: Member '{0}' specified in OptionalRequired attribute does not exist in type '{1}'

data.name: InvalidOptionalMemberDescription
data.value: All members specified in OptionalRequired attribute must exist in the declaring type.

data.name: RedundantOptionalMemberMessageFormat

data.name: RedundantOptionalMemberDescription
data.value: Members that are assigned in the constructor should not be specified in OptionalRequired attribute.
